NOTE ON THE CONTENTS OF THIS ARCHIVE:

The two enclosed .ZIP files comprise all necessary source to
Turbo Vision 2.0.  Note that no path information is stored in
these archive.  Typically, the contents of INCLUDE.ZIP are to 
be placed in \BCx\INCLUDE\TVISION;  the contents of SOURCE.ZIP 
are to be placed in \BCx\SOURCE\TVISION.  Also note that the 
source includes some assembly language (*.ASM) files.  Success-
ful generation of the Turbo Vision library will require use of 
Turbo Assembler to translate these source code files into ob-
ject files.
